[
    {
        "content": "<p>How do I show the vertical line at character 100 in VSCode on a non-mathlib project?</p>",
        "id": 310859914,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1668788843
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If possible, in a way that's persistent across instances of VSCode</p>",
        "id": 310860006,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1668788870
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>See <code>.vscode/settings.json</code> in mathlib for some good defaults</p>",
        "id": 310860420,
        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1668788986
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You need to add</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"s2\">\"editorRuler.foreground\"</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"#ff40efa1\"</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>(this is my favourite color) as well as </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"s2\">\"editor.rulers\"</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span> <span class=\"mi\">100</span><span class=\"o\">],</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>in your <code>json</code> file.</p>",
        "id": 310860425,
        "sender_full_name": "Filippo A. E. Nuccio",
        "timestamp": 1668788990
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Amazing! Worked instantly.</p>",
        "id": 310863262,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1668789769
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Well, had it worked after a couple of hours, I would have doubted of my understanding on how software works... <span aria-label=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f601\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning face with smiling eyes\">:grinning_face_with_smiling_eyes:</span></p>",
        "id": 310863440,
        "sender_full_name": "Filippo A. E. Nuccio",
        "timestamp": 1668789826
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I mean I didn't have to restart VSCode <span aria-label=\"grinning\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f600\" role=\"img\" title=\"grinning\">:grinning:</span></p>",
